However, Solbes found in the halls of the Congress building that even if the present number is not good, the inflation difference between Spain and the other members of the monetary union has remained more or less the same in recent years.
He also said that in November there were less surprises than in the previous month, where the government did not expect such a high increase.
We expected a value of about 4%, the Minister for Economic and Financial Affairs announced with regard to the forecast published today.
